NC.Q: Between 1966 and 1970, was the average total Warehouse Utilization higher or lower than between 1965 and 1967?
NC.A: The average total warehouse utilization between 1966 and 1970 was {lower} than between 1965 and 1967.

NC.Q: Was the total Warehouse Utilization in 1964 higher or lower than in 1976?
NC.A: The total warehouse utilization in 1964 was {higher} than in 1976.

NC.Q: Between 1969 and 1976, did the total Warehouse Utilization experience a larger or smaller change than between 1965 and 1969?
